      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "Well-kept, honest example in good overall condition. It runs and drives well, presents nicely inside and out, and should make a very satisfying driver for someone who wants a quality car without paying top-tier money for a mint showpiece. Expect a clean, solid vehicle with normal age-appropriate wear, but overall it has clearly been cared for and is above average in appearance and usability.",
