    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "Clean, honest car in good condition and a great choice for someone who wants a solid driver they can enjoy right away. It presents well, has clearly been cared for, and shows the kind of light age and use you\u2019d expect from a good-quality example rather than a show car. A fun, attractive car with plenty of appeal and a nice step up from the average project or fair-condition driver.",
