    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Solid, well-kept car in good overall condition. It presents nicely, runs and drives the way a good honest example should, and is the kind of car you can enjoy right away without it feeling like an unfinished project. The exterior and interior both show well for the age, though you should still expect some minor cosmetic wear and small imperfections consistent with a used vehicle rather than a mint, fully restored show car. Overall, this is a strong driver-quality example for someone who wants a car that is above average in condition, attractive, and usable now.",
